<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span> <span class="c2">«الْحَيَاءُ مِنَ الْإِيمَانِ»</span> وَ <span class="c2">«الْحَيَاءُ شُعْبَةٌ مِنَ الْإِيمَانِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>